sc.view

Class CalculatorOverviewController

  • java.lang.Object
    • sc.view.CalculatorOverviewController

  • public class CalculatorOverviewController
extends java.lang.Object
    CalculatorOverviewController is a part of the view of SimpleCount application.

    His task is to receive any user action (click, select a button, keyboard input, etc.). These events are sent to the controller.

    1.0
